OCC: I am not sure if the person controling phobia saw this post. I sent it 
three days ago. I find it fairly important. So please reply in some way....

      Death glided across the floor. He had been trained by the best assasins 
in the universe. He was the instrument of Hades. He walked past the bridge 
and saw a bot sitting in a chair. He had been taught how to invade a bots 
datatracks with out any way of them detecting them doing so. Death lunged 
back as he saw the images of the wrongs he had done. In the customs of his 
faith. He chose this bot to die. He had been taught by the one called Unicron 
the art of silence. No one could hear or follow him. He was undetectable by 
the naked ear. He glided onto the bridge...behind the bot. Not so close so he 
could detect his presence. He put the  reaper 1 inch from the back of the 
bots neck. The reaper could cut through pure energon. He pulled it back very 
slowly. In full force he pushed it at the back of the bots neck.... proceeded 
to  cut off the bots head.......
